#Text=DeMar DeRozan led the way for the Raptors ( 44 - 29 ) with 18 points , six assists , three rebounds and one steal , in 37 minutes .

#Text=Serge Ibaka followed up with 18 points , eight rebounds , one assist and one steal , in 32 minutes , while Jonas Valanciunas chipped in 18 points , six rebounds , one assist and one steal , in 22 minutes .

#Text=The Raptors will look to bounce back as they play host to the Trail Blazers on Monday .
#Text=Meanwhile , the Mavericks ( 31 - 41 ) have now lost four of their last five games , as they continue to battle for the top seed in the West .
